{"tid":1925854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［尋找苦主］過完數即block人間蒸發走數！！！","createTime":"2020-03-14T16:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:52:39.000Z","uid":177214,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"510b691cb5455a4cddb79784d763140056acb40b","tid":1925854,"uid":177214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r42ZdmV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr42ZdmV.png&h=60885914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詳細係我係fb鞋谷徵鞋，比尼個人inbox<br />\n傾左一大輪，講好哂價錢比哂相約交收既時候<br />\n聲稱自己住澳門，近排過境面交唔方便..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOTxyFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOTxyFH.png&h=570b93de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得出結論係順豐寄比我，我當時覺得過數再寄，好冇保障，say左no，對話如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uCZdG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCZdG8.png&h=35d71eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都應成左先過一半數收到貨過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygXN63t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygXN63t.png&h=fb98a3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過完數之後，做戲做全套，問埋郵寄詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaYd2Ez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaYd2Ez.png&h=ec848e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對話就到尼到，跟住就秒block左我，完全聯絡唔到<br />\n宜家心頭上得佢個轉數快no. 同hsbc 戶口<br />\n已經打算去報案，亦都係希望當時人睇到主動聯絡反還反錢（雖然冇乜可能）<br />\n<br />\n亦都想靠連登尼個平台睇下搵唔搵到其他比佢呃左既人同苦主，睇下有冇同路人<br />\n一齊有報案no.，相信警察個邊做野都會快d<br />\n<br />\n預左比各位屌傻仔，屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我最重要既想睇下宜家有冇咩方法可以做到，唔想再有下個受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1427b5c1635f21eb3074ba0e00a42007cfc84e0","tid":1925854,"uid":36995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"一手交錢 一手交貨<br />\n咁都仲有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c747df4fc61c5c3163251faa008d32cad531a7","tid":1925854,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1427b5c1635f21eb3074ba0e00a42007cfc84e0","tid":1925854,"uid":36995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"一手交錢 一手交貨<br />\n咁都仲有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"3a6e8ce118c5689ce27f7ca2ca6c8c39135e2551","tid":1925854,"uid":36049,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"又一單弱智發現案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b3c6729361964ee320b16fdcc38e3e7e7b406f","tid":1925854,"uid":177214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1427b5c1635f21eb3074ba0e00a42007cfc84e0","tid":1925854,"uid":36995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"一手交錢 一手交貨<br />\n咁都仲有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"都知自己on9左<br />\n宜家打算禮拜一去銀行搞齊資料<br />\n去報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f368386b38100987522383575ceecd84513db311","tid":1925854,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"又係過數黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151c18e5219cf4aa395879b50295ffa4ff74eb00","tid":1925854,"uid":81256,"l